<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l25">fürt vnd auch vns mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> brıef nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd begert hat . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
