</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="54r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Winsheim und von Sweinfürt, yeder stat also
                            <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        durlewchtigst fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund,</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.
                        künig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit,</ex></expan> den von Sweinfürt und auch uns mit
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> brief nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und begert hat,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<add>bey seinen <expan>küniglich<ex>en</ex></expan> gnaden</add> in dem
                                <expan>co<ex>n</ex>cilio</expan>
<add>zu</add> Costencz zu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als ir an der
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> seins briefs, die wir ewch
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mals in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>
                        gesent <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wol <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, also tun wir ewch zu wissen, daz wir kürczlich willen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde
                        und erber <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                        gen Costencz zu schiken. Da mugt ir ewch wol wissen nach zu richten. Denn wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
